{"tid":569874,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「支那人來了末日就不遠」 哈薩克民族主義者抗議向支那靠攏","createTime":"2018-02-23T06:17:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-24T09:23:53.000Z","uid":60545,"like":51,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a76c89cfb3d66e8505f38ac71843bf66f140ece0","tid":569874,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T06:17:22.000Z","msg":"大陸和哈薩克的合作不僅重塑全球交通路線，隨著中國深入深受俄羅斯影響的哈薩克腹地之際，也將動搖哈薩克和全球的政治。在內陸國哈薩克上建立不近海的「無水港」（dry port）作為交通樞紐，也涉及昂貴的社會工程。<br />\n<br />\n經營無水港的公司執行長哈姆津（Zhaslan Khamzin）表示，中國人「不是傻瓜，商人錙銖必較，他們若要在這投資，他們知道5或10年就可連本帶利賺回來。」<br />\n<br />\n哈薩克是中亞最大最富庶的國家，1991年蘇聯解體後獨立，之後一直努力和俄國保持友好關係，但近年與大陸擴展關係時，也逐漸損及俄國主宰的地位。<br />\n<br />\n哈薩克親大陸的轉變在國內引發不少騷動，哈薩克深根蒂固的反對情緒源自蘇聯時期的文宣，和幾百年來對大陸的恐懼。哈薩克族民族主義者抗議表示，國家從俄國獨立，現在又要繞著大陸轉，該族有句諺語：「中國人來了，末日就不遠了。」<br />\n<br />\n在努爾干鎮工作的大陸人則認為，沒什麼可以阻止大陸勢力進入哈薩克，「管他是海運還是火車，只要目前情況繼續下去，對我們都沒差。」<br />\n<br />\n哈薩克跟大陸一樣投入巨額政治資本打造新絲路，這項計畫讓哈薩克和大陸在經濟上更緊密合作，雖然許多哈薩克國民心存疑慮，但對於哈薩克領袖，這是制衡俄國影響力的唯一可行方式。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6811/2984256\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6811%2F2984256&d=czLhboHiFNV%2BMEKCeGGQ0wHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=559e6907\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6811/2984256</a><br />\n<br />\n英語原文 <strong>China&rsquo;s Ambitious New &lsquo;Port&rsquo;: Landlocked Kazakhstan</strong> by New York Times<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mobile.nytimes.com/2018/01/01/world/asia/china-kazakhstan-silk-road.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.nytimes.com%2F2018%2F01%2F01%2Fworld%2Fasia%2Fchina-kazakhstan-silk-road.html&d=czLhboHiFNV%2BMEKCeGGQ0wHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=7824aa4b\" target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.nytimes.com/2018/01/01/world/asia/china-kazakhstan-silk-road.html</a>"},{"pid":"c6d1c0e6561bade1e610c980c63160eacc9d7bd8","tid":569874,"uid":37661,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T06:19:30.000Z","msg":"咪撚放寬支那去哈薩克簽證呀<br />\n<br />\n愈難申請愈好。"},{"pid":"2d27e6223aeb72c5cb5e2b4d08e5f17319fd0a53","tid":569874,"uid":60545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T06:22:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5ef92171b2552e47986dba076f6ddb4b3601665","tid":569874,"uid":55913,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T06:26:53.000Z","msg":"喂 一帶一路<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf781d15a917261ab54c10ff36245374b1e04bde","tid":569874,"uid":60545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T06:44:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"198bc265f005cac7377a785bad8c4729f15cf436","tid":569874,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T06:45:15.000Z","msg":"咁似傳教口號 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69c55cf7a7267702fadfe4d68dc833990a611981","tid":569874,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T06:47:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35b9b7eed787c1f8a0c26d9d0c548ba82ccc28f9","tid":569874,"uid":54812,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T06:49:39.000Z","msg":"傷害13億蝗蟲感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acb641dd674f15cae9a998b5ca96815ef7506387","tid":569874,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35b9b7eed787c1f8a0c26d9d0c548ba82ccc28f9","tid":569874,"uid":54812,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T06:49:39.000Z","msg":"傷害13億蝗蟲感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T06:50:25.000Z","msg":"入侵哈薩克未<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgm